videos.description: Oklahoma's Gabbi Ortiz tosses a great pass up court to Peyton Little who lays it in and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Ortiz's great pass sets up a Little score and foul

videos.description: Oklahoma's Peyton Little steals a pass, then up court gives to Gabbi Ortiz who sinks a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Defense creates offense for Oklahoma

videos.description: Baylor's Alexis Jones attacks the lane, lays it in, and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Jones streaks past the Oklahoma defense for the score

videos.description: Off a long rebound, Baylor's Kalani Brown is wide open underneath the basket to score.
videos.headline: Brown wide open for the easy lay-in

videos.description: Alexis Jones steals a pass, hustles up court, then scores and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Jones does it all for Baylor on a  3-point play

videos.description: Baylor's Alexis Jones completes a triple-double after assisting on a Kalani Brown score.
videos.headline: Brown layup gives Jones triple-double

videos.description: Baylor's Alexis Jones breaks down her triple-double performance.
